thread.title_full: Public Storage reviewed by Kim Wheeler

author: Kim Wheeler
title: Kim Wheeler
text: From my reservation to the actual renting my storage unit, Keona (sp?) was extremely helpful, very professional, above and beyond the standard professional I expected. I was so relieved with all the help with selecting a unit I needed and the availabilty of the unit. She was just amazing.
